headline: LifeStyles Healthcare Appoints Peter Luther to Board of Directors
summary: LifeStyles Healthcare ("LifeStyles"), a global intimate health and wellness platform, and Linden Capital Partners portfolio company, is pleased to announce the appointment of Peter Luther to its Board of Directors.
